column2: SELECT ra, dec FROM MyDB.ISOLATED_ZOOSPECDR1#_IN OPEN my_cursor WHILE (# = #) BEGIN FETCH NEXT from my_cursor into @ra, @dec IF (@@fetch_status < #) break INSERT MYDB.ISOLATED_ZOOSPECDR1#_OUT SELECT @ra, @dec, p.ra, p.dec, p.objID, gz.spiral, gz.elliptical, gz.uncertain FROM dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (@ra, @dec, #/#) n, Galaxy p JOIN Photoz As z ON z.objid = p.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN zooSpec AS gz ON gz.objid = p.objid WHERE n.objid = p.objid END CLOSE my_cursor DEALLOCATE my_cursor
